<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 08:10:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯：内塔尼亚胡关于部分协议的声明证明以色列拒绝停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-live/top-u-s-military-officer-says-israeli-offensive-in-lebanon-risks-iranian-response/00000190-4843-d91c-abba-ef5325930000</link><description>以色列国防军在加沙杀死了哈马斯高级成员，他是该组织弹药生产工作的关键人物 ■ 反政府抗议者堵塞以色列中央高速公路上的交通，呼吁举行选举 ■ 美国高级军官表示，美国可能无法保护以色列免受真主党的袭击，例如以色列在梅图拉被黎巴嫩反坦克火力打成重伤，另一名以色列人受轻伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-live/top-u-s-military-officer-says-israeli-offensive-in-lebanon-risks-iranian-response/00000190-4843-d91c-abba-ef5325930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正危险地接近三线战争：加沙、黎巴嫩和约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-damages-sensitive-relations-with-u-s-as-war-with-hezbollah-looms/00000190-4663-d91c-abba-ef73f4440000</link><description>在北方爆发全面战争的边缘，内塔尼亚胡选择公开攻击拜登政府推迟向以色列运送武器，首先是为了迎合他的右翼基础。国防部长约阿夫·加兰特将在访问华盛顿期间努力解决交付危机</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-damages-sensitive-relations-with-u-s-as-war-with-hezbollah-looms/00000190-4663-d91c-abba-ef73f4440000</guid></item><item><title>美国断然拒绝内塔尼亚胡关于故意减少武器运输的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/u-s-outright-rejects-pms-claims-about-arms-shipments/00000190-46a9-dafc-adb4-77e917cb0000</link><description>以色列高级官员表示，最近几周发货量有所放缓，他们认为这是由于官僚和技术问题造成的。一名高级官员称，鉴于北部紧张局势日益加剧，内塔尼亚胡攻击政府的决定是“危险的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/u-s-outright-rejects-pms-claims-about-arms-shipments/00000190-46a9-dafc-adb4-77e917cb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府推进法案永久禁止半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-government-advances-bill-making-al-jazeera-ban-permanent/00000190-4686-d768-adf8-4eb6eaa50000</link><description>该临时命令目前有效期至 7 月 31 日，或至国内特殊情况声明结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-government-advances-bill-making-al-jazeera-ban-permanent/00000190-4686-d768-adf8-4eb6eaa50000</guid></item><item><title>由于新的变种，以色列的冠状病毒病例有所增加，引发了新的疫苗接种工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/coronavirus-cases-rising-in-israel-due-to-new-variants-sparking-new-vaccination-effort/00000190-4664-d16c-a7b0-5eed47970000</link><description>以色列疾病预防控制中心和公共卫生官员报告称，最近几周病例数量“非常显着”增加，但数据中没有反映出来，因为“社区几乎没有进行检测”。本地增长与国外模式一致</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 19:21:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/coronavirus-cases-rising-in-israel-due-to-new-variants-sparking-new-vaccination-effort/00000190-4664-d16c-a7b0-5eed47970000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡最担心的三个问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-23/ty-article/.highlight/the-three-questions-netanyahu-fears-most/00000190-4612-d429-abfc-7f5251aa0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的喉舌第14频道罕见地接受了以色列媒体的采访，但他永远不会问他这三个问题。只能希望能够采访他的美国记者</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 19:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-23/ty-article/.highlight/the-three-questions-netanyahu-fears-most/00000190-4612-d429-abfc-7f5251aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长：这么长时间未能任命最高法院院长是前所未有的监督</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-failure-to-appoint-supreme-court-president-for-so-long-is-unprecedented/00000190-4645-d91c-abba-ef55b7b60000</link><description>在回应要求以色列司法部长选择最高法院常任院长的上诉时，以色列总检察长表示，这一拖延严重损害了司法机构和权力分立原则</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:42:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-failure-to-appoint-supreme-court-president-for-so-long-is-unprecedented/00000190-4645-d91c-abba-ef55b7b60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院命令政府披露斯德泰曼监狱加沙被拘留者的状况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-state-must-reveal-conditions-of-gaza-detainees-at-sde-teiman-prison/00000190-45c7-d8cb-a19d-4dc718ac0000</link><description>尽管通知高等法院它将把所有被拘留者从该地点移走，但该国仍将被要求解决斯德泰曼拘留设施中巴勒斯坦人的医疗、惩罚方法和手铐条件等问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 17:25:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-state-must-reveal-conditions-of-gaza-detainees-at-sde-teiman-prison/00000190-45c7-d8cb-a19d-4dc718ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 261 天：以色列国防军士兵在真主党无人机袭击中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-261-idf-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/00000190-4609-d768-adf8-4ebbc0af0000</link><description>消息人士告诉《国土报》，卡塔尔与哈马斯举行直接会谈，以弥合当前停火提案与该组织深远要求之间的差距。 ■ 真主党发布视频，声称显示以色列军事和战略设施的卫星镜头。 ■ 以色列公设辩护人办公室谴责以色列警方的行为针对反政府抗议者的暴力行为 ■ 战争进入 261 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 17:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-261-idf-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/00000190-4609-d768-adf8-4ebbc0af0000</guid></item><item><title>“AOC 你无法隐藏”：亲巴勒斯坦团体在纽约鲍曼集会上瞄准奥卡西奥-科尔特斯和桑德斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pro-palestinian-group-targets-ocasio-cortez-and-sanders-at-bowman-rally-in-nyc/00000190-44e5-d768-adf8-4cf799c00000</link><description>10 月 7 日，支持巴勒斯坦“一切形式”抵抗的强硬派组织“我们的一生”在众议员贾马尔·鲍曼 (Jamaal Bowman) 的预选会上出现，抗议以色列的进步批评者 - 它认为以色列是“犹太复国主义者”布朗克斯集会。鲍曼正面临 AIPAC 对他前所未有的支出狂潮</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 16:11:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pro-palestinian-group-targets-ocasio-cortez-and-sanders-at-bowman-rally-in-nyc/00000190-44e5-d768-adf8-4cf799c00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡关键部长米里·雷格夫因在加沙战争期间前往希腊度假而受到批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/key-netanyahu-minister-miri-regev-blasted-for-vacationing-in-greece-amid-gaza-war/00000190-4594-d429-abfc-7dd63ef10000</link><description>以色列交通部长米里·雷格夫 (Miri Regev) 对希腊进行了私人访问，此前她于 2 月份前往印度和斯里兰卡度假，花费总计约 12 万美元，引发了众怒。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 15:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/key-netanyahu-minister-miri-regev-blasted-for-vacationing-in-greece-amid-gaza-war/00000190-4594-d429-abfc-7dd63ef10000</guid></item><item><title>报告：真主党在贝鲁特民用机场储存伊朗武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/report-hezbollah-storing-iranian-weapons-ammo-in-beiruts-civil-airport/00000190-4563-dafc-adb4-75eb04f60000</link><description>《每日电讯报》报道真主党在贝鲁特拉菲克·哈里里国际机场囤积伊朗武器后，以色列军队表示，如果真主党从该机场袭击平民，以色列军队“别无选择，只能做出回应”</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 15:24:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/report-hezbollah-storing-iranian-weapons-ammo-in-beiruts-civil-airport/00000190-4563-dafc-adb4-75eb04f60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡任命前以色列国防军司令领导以色列北部的重建工作，以应对与真主党的冲突升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-appoints-former-idf-navy-chief-to-lead-north-israels-rehabilitation/00000190-455c-d768-adf8-4dfe5a310000</link><description>在与真主党发生数月冲突后，以色列北部的重建工作将由埃利泽·马罗姆领导，他在周日接受采访时表示，以色列人需要国际保证才能在黎巴嫩南部不发动军事行动的情况下返回北部</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 14:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-appoints-former-idf-navy-chief-to-lead-north-israels-rehabilitation/00000190-455c-d768-adf8-4dfe5a310000</guid></item><item><title>警察暴行加剧，以色列警察在反政府抗议活动中推搡记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-shoves-journalist-at-anti-govt-protest-amid-rising-police-brutality/00000190-4536-d91c-abba-ef367dae0000</link><description>在特拉维夫举行的一场反对总理内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动中，一名警察被看到暴力推搡一名明显是记者的妇女，以色列警方发表正式声明，对这一事件表示歉意</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 14:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-shoves-journalist-at-anti-govt-protest-amid-rising-police-brutality/00000190-4536-d91c-abba-ef367dae0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡加大力度回应美国批评，称大部分弹药尚未抵达</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-doubles-down-on-u-s-criticism-says-most-munitions-yet-to-arrive/00000190-44e9-d429-abfc-7dfbe64e0000</link><description>总理为其公开批评美国的决定进行了辩护，称“从美国运往以色列的弹药大幅减少” ■ 国防部长加兰特将在华盛顿会见美国高级官员</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 13:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-doubles-down-on-u-s-criticism-says-most-munitions-yet-to-arrive/00000190-44e9-d429-abfc-7dfbe64e0000</guid></item><item><title>宝贝，在以色列进行钻探：福音派石油公司在以色列启动了另一项勘探项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/drill-baby-in-israel-evangelical-oil-company-launches-exploration-venture-in-israel/00000190-44e5-dafc-adb4-75ed4fab0000</link><description>锡安石油和天然气公司由一位美国基督徒创立，他表示希望促进以色列的能源独立，以帮助犹太人民</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 12:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/drill-baby-in-israel-evangelical-oil-company-launches-exploration-venture-in-israel/00000190-44e5-dafc-adb4-75ed4fab0000</guid></item><item><title>公设辩护人办公室：警察暴力践踏以色列人的人权，必须停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/public-defenders-office-police-violence-tramples-human-rights-must-be-stopped/00000190-4478-da42-a1ba-7f7a5e330000</link><description>公设辩护人办公室的一名高级官员在对抗议活动的首次公开反应中表示，警察暴力是“对暴力警察不执法、对违法警察视而不见、宽大处理的结果”</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 11:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/public-defenders-office-police-violence-tramples-human-rights-must-be-stopped/00000190-4478-da42-a1ba-7f7a5e330000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列人被黎巴嫩的反坦克火力打伤；内塔尼亚胡：加沙“激烈”的战斗即将结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-live/u-s-military-say-they-destroyed-three-houthi-vessels-in-red-sea/00000190-4301-d768-adf8-4fb3a7ac0000</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡：加沙部分地区的激烈战斗即将结束 ■ 当地市政府称，黎巴嫩反坦克炮火造成两人轻伤 ■ 真主党声称对向上加利利发射的无人机负责 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，自战争以来，有 37,598 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙地带丧生■ 内塔尼亚胡谈美国扣押武器：“主要群众留下来”</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-live/u-s-military-say-they-destroyed-three-houthi-vessels-in-red-sea/00000190-4301-d768-adf8-4fb3a7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，以色列士兵在加沙南部行动事故中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-operational-accident-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-4185-d8cb-a19d-49c7e91d0000</link><description>中士。一等兵马尔基亚·格罗斯 (Malkia Gross)，25 岁​​，来自约旦河西岸定居点苏西亚 (Susya)，在加沙南部被杀。格罗斯是一名数学老师，是苏西亚在战争中丧生的第四名士兵</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:43:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-operational-accident-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-4185-d8cb-a19d-49c7e91d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔向哈马斯施压，要求其放弃与以色列达成人质协议的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/qatar-pressuring-hamas-to-walk-back-its-demands-for-hostage-deal-with-israel/00000190-415e-d8cb-a19d-495ffe430000</link><description>停火和人质协议的谈判正在进行中，但以色列消息人士对进展感到悲观，称哈马斯目前对达成协议兴趣不大。卡塔尔正试图利用哈马斯放弃其最深远的要求，以期达成协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/qatar-pressuring-hamas-to-walk-back-its-demands-for-hostage-deal-with-israel/00000190-415e-d8cb-a19d-495ffe430000</guid></item></channel></rss>